Subtitle of Senate Bill 464
TO AMEND THE LAWS CONCERNING SALES OF RAW MILK; AND TO ALLOW SALES
OF RAW MILK AND RAW MILK PRODUCTS AT LOCATIONS OTHER THAN THE FARM
WHERE THE RAW MILK OR RAW MILK PRODUCT IS PRODUCED.
______________________________________________________________________
Amendment No. 1 to Senate Bill 464
Amend Senate Bill 464 as originally introduced:
Page 1, line 12, delete "PRODUCED;" and substitute "PRODUCED; TO DECLARE AN
EMERGENCY;"
AND
Delete the subtitle in its entirety and substitute:
"TO AMEND THE LAWS CONCERNING SALES OF
RAW MILK; TO ALLOW SALES OF RAW MILK AND
RAW MILK PRODUCTS AT LOCATIONS OTHER THAN
THE FARM WHERE THE RAW MILK OR RAW MILK
PRODUCT WAS PRODUCED; AND TO DECLARE AN
EMERGENCY."
AND
Page 3, delete line 27, and substitute the following:
"consumption of the raw milk product.
SECTION 2. EMERGENCY CLAUSE. It is found and determined by the
General Assembly of the State of Arkansas that under present state law, raw
